data.description: Welcome to your completely renovated, all brick ranch home with first floor living! Walk in to your large remodeled kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, an a breakfast nook, and modern lighting. Continue into the dining and living room with hard wood floors, open and overlooking your private backyard! Take the sliders out of the living room or family room, with wood burning fireplace, to enjoy an almost completely fenced off, peaceful sanctuary off of your patio! The master bedroom has a full en suite bath. 2 generously sized bedrooms are also available with a renovated bathroom off of the hallway. Next you’ll be impressed with the finished basement! A large space for entertaining, fully finished, and with a large storage space! And if this isn’t enough, a huge 2 car garage! New furnace 2021- New hot water tank! Basement Waterproofed - 2009! Attached 2 Car Garage! New Hot Water Tank - August 2019! New Roof in 2008 & New Windows in 2009! And for peace of mind, a home warranty is provided.
